data.text:
I'm born in Sequals in 1947(Pordenone - Italy).

I know that my family doesn't come from this part of Italy (perhaps Sicily?).

My parents are Giovanni Galante(1915-1989) and Angela Bernardin.

The name of my grand-father was Gio-Batta Galante(1890-1963 + of -).

I would like to know my origins.

Thanks for help.
